title: Jury acquits two men in Michigan governor kidnapping case, deadlocks on two others - Reuters.com

description: A federal jury on Friday acquitted two men of conspiring to kidnap Michigan Governor Gretchen Whitmer in 2020 and the judge overseeing the case declared a mistrial for two other men after jurors could not come to a verdict for them.
